# InvoiceCreated.thunder
# Event intent: the published contract other services react to.

event InvoiceCreated

why
  Downstream services react to new invoices, so the contract must be stable.

publishedBy
  BillingService

consumedBy
  NotificationService
  ReportingService

payload
  invoiceId: InvoiceId
  customerId: CustomerId
  total: Money

guarantees
  event is idempotent
  event contains no payment secrets

guarantee event contains no payment secrets
  because event streams are widely readable across the platform
  verify security scan

never
  include payment token in payload

verify
  contract check
  security scan
